# Level Definition file
# X solid wall
# - place where an item or a monster can be placed
# T transparrent, free place which can not be passed by monster or player
# P possible player position
# p alternative player position
# E exit
# D all 'D's have to be hit by bomb before the Exit opens
# F free place which can be passed by monster or player, but no items or monsters placed here when level starts


